My PMI

Supported languages: English-US, English-UK, English-CA, English-AU
Watch, listen, read project management-related content on the new My PMI Application. 
Customers may use the Alexa personal assistant, with their connected Echo Dot, to access and download content.

The current version is supported only on Amazon Echo Dot.
